notes.title: Apple Unveils New AI Features
notes.content:
## Apple AI Event Summary (May 2025)

Apple just announced a set of **AI-powered features** for iOS 19:

- **Smart Compose** in Messages
- Personalized Siri powered by Apple Neural Engine
- System-wide summarization

> Tim Cook emphasized Apple’s privacy-first approach to AI.

More details coming at WWDC next month.

notes.title: SpaceX Starship Launch Update
notes.content:
### Starship’s 4th Test Flight

SpaceX successfully launched its **fourth full-stack Starship** from Boca Chica. Key points:

- Reached orbit, but experienced engine shutdown during reentry.
- SpaceX confirmed this was the most successful test yet.

Elon tweeted:
> “Next one will stick the landing.”

notes.title: AI Regulation Bill Passed
notes.content:
#### US Senate Approves First AI Regulation

The **Artificial Intelligence Safety & Standards Act** passed with bipartisan support. Highlights:

- Mandatory audits for LLMs with over 1 billion parameters.
- Restrictions on AI-generated political content.
- Transparency requirements for AI models.

Tech firms are expected to **lobby for amendments** before the bill is signed into law.
